OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly
OL,6,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight, heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes in the west. Mainly dry towards
OL,9,Fthe Moray Firth and Speyside.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FCloudy with further outbreaks
OL,12,Fof rain in the morning across the
OL,13,Fwest, becoming drier through the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Dry in the east with some
OL,15,Fbright spells.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,18,Fdry with sunny spells and isolated
OL,19,Fshowers on Tuesday. Dry with sunny
OL,20,Fspells and becoming increasingly warm
OL,21,Fduring Wednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
